  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="eyebrow">404</p>
      <h1>页面未找到</h1>
      <p class="lead">这个链接可能已经移动。可以从首页、州指南或专题目录重新开始。</p>
      <div class="card-actions">
        <a class="button-link primary" href="/">回到首页</a>
        <a class="button-link secondary" href="/states/">州指南</a>
        <a class="button-link secondary" href="/topics/">专题</a>
      </div>
    </div>
